{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-plugin-webpack-size","description":"Logs your production bundle sizes in a CI friendly way","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","webpack","bundle"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"axe312","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/9deffeac1bef56ed97c1fa509c7204d2"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/axe312ger/gatsby-plugin-webpack-size"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-plugin-webpack-size\"><a href=\"#gatsby-plugin-webpack-size\" aria-label=\"gatsby plugin webpack size permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gatsby Plugin Webpack Size</h1>\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/gatsby-plugin-webpack-size\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/npm/v/gatsby-plugin-webpack-size.svg\" alt=\"NPM\">\n  </a>\n  &#xA0;\n  <a href=\"http://npm-stat.com/charts.html?package=gatsby-plugin-webpack-size\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/npm/dm/gatsby-plugin-webpack-size.svg\" alt=\"NPM downloads\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Implements CI friendly bundle size logging for your production builds.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"./screenshot.png\" alt=\"Screenshot\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"️installation\"><a href=\"#%EF%B8%8Finstallation\" aria-label=\"️installation permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>☁️ Installation</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">npm i gatsby-plugin-webpack-size</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"setup\"><a href=\"#setup\" aria-label=\"setup permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>🛫 Setup</h2>\n<p>Add <code class=\"language-text\">&#39;gatsby-plugin-webpack-size&#39;</code> to the plugins in your <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code> file.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-plugin-webpack-size`</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"️configuration\"><a href=\"#%EF%B8%8Fconfiguration\" aria-label=\"️configuration permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>⚙️ Configuration</h2>\n<p>The only custom option implemented is <code class=\"language-text\">development</code>. All other options are passed to the <a href=\"https://github.com/GoogleChromeLabs/size-plugin\">size-plugin</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n      <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-plugin-webpack-size`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// Set to true to show bundle sizes in development mode as well</span>\n        development<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-plugin-webpack-size/","id":"c9c3cf7d-a56e-5c5c-a8c5-2c89b222e089","layout":"plugins"}}